              "concept_source": "Is + [name] + a + [adjective] + [noun]?",
              "concept_target": "[TRANSLATE]",
              "explanation_source": "In English, the adjective comes BEFORE the noun. So we say 'a big city', not 'a city big'. To ask a yes/no question, put 'Is' at the start: 'Is Pasadena a big city?'",
